name: Tempura Shibe
description:
"To catch a shrimp tempura, you must first be a shrimp tempura".
Shibe didn't remember who said it, but he thought it makes sense, so he rented a shrimp tempura costume and jumped into a giant noodle bowl where some shrimp tempuras lived. He is very happy he got to catch one.

Originally a submission for #LetsRaiseTheWoof art competition by SuperShiba club!

4000 x 4000 px
